content: Thank you for the additional information. According to the details you provided, the parents of Lavalette Miller were Joseph Miller and Florence Tice. Joseph Miller was born in Virginia in 1848, and Florence Tice was born in Maryland in 1857. They were married on September 7, 1876, in Washington County, Maryland. Lavalette Miller was born to them on July 3, 1878, in Hagerstown, Washington County, Maryland.
